cessories, that heavily feature cultural motifs and will be worn during the opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"the striking designs\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"intricately embroidered vests\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"dresses\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"accessories\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural motifs\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 425}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TikTokerRyan Yip, whose video on the outfits drew more than 424,500 likes, lovingly deemed the aesthetic \\\"sorcery.\\\"\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TikTokerRyan Yip\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"whose video\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"the outfits\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 424,500 likes\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"the aesthetic \\\"sorcery\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tell me what motivated [Michel & Amazonka] and the whole of Mongolian Olympic team to pop off that hard,\\\" Yip said.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 662, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\", \"score\": 0.9983060211629822, \"rank\": 0.0008629539118200387, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yip\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another TikToker, who goes byRegularguy_sports, ranked Team Mongolia first in a list of top Olympic uniforms.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://